{
  "stem": "15174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had large areas, large holds, so I guess it was for transporting goods from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't know how many passengers there were, but there were quite a few.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother and the women were in the one huge room on deck, but my father and I and all the men were in the hold, right near the engine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, we-- you know, we were happy to be on the ship, but I was seasick on that ship from the moment we left Lisbon to the moment we got to New York.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't sleep in the hold because it was hot as hell, and people were vomiting all the time, and the smell was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So when it wasn't pouring we would sleep on the deck just because-- because it was impossible to sleep in-- in the-- in the hold.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We stop in Bermuda for about a week and all the passengers were interrogated by British Intelligence, which was interesting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Even I-- the kids went and were interrogated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, you know, I felt really important.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Here was this solider, he was interrogating me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He wanted to know if I knew anything that would be of interest as far as military operations were concerned.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he asked me specific questions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I remembered he asked me if there was a power plant near where we lived in France, and I-- I-- I said yes, there is, and I told him about it and where exactly it was and so on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I felt very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we were in Bermuda for a week, and then we set sail and we arrived in New York on June 24, 1942.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
